      "title": "HNBGI holds series of mini awards ceremonies",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Highlights from the series of mini awards ceremonies of HNBGI",
        "With the objective of acknowledging the remarkable efforts and empowering, supporting, and accelerating the performance of the Multi-Channel Business Network inclusive of the Agency Channel, Corporate Sales Division, Bancassurance and Broker Divisions, HNB General Insurance Ltd. (HNBGI) held a series of mini awards ceremonies in Galle, Kandy and Colombo recently.",
        "This series of mini award ceremonies were held with the participation of the senior management of HNBGI.",
        "CEO Sithumina Jayasundara said: \u201cThemed \u2018Celebrating Excellence\u2019, this series of events were held to applaud all the hard work, commitment and dedication of our champs across all the business channels over the last two years. HNBGI has reached a number of milestones during the year as well and our Sales Teams together with the Corporate Sales Division, Bancassurance and Broker Divisions contributed towards achieving an outstanding performance thus far.\u201d",
        "\u201cAs we have started to witness the aftermath impact of a global pandemic coupled with an economic crisis, it is vital to inculcate team spirit, togetherness and a sense of guidance across every team in the organisation. While the business will remain dynamic and resilient, with the direction of the management and contribution of the Agency Channel along with the rest of the Sales Channels, I\u2019m sure that HNBGI will continue its growth momentum and reach greater heights in its journey.\u201d",
        "\u201cWhilst appreciating the Agency and Sales Channels for their relentless commitment, dedication and all the hard work, I\u2019m confident that as one team with a common goal driven by shared values, we will be able to take the business to the next level in terms of service excellence, operational excellence and product excellence,\u201d he added."
      ],
